package machinelearningproject
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    CSVReader
    This is a class which extends FileReader, and implements a constructor and overrides an abstract method.
    DataAnalyser
    This is a class that is used to perform methods which separates the data of a CSV file into easier variables to manipulate such as columns, features and rows.
    Main
    This is the main class of the program which can be used to peform Naive Bayes in the command line.
    NaiveBayes
    This is a class that is used to perform the Naive Bayes Machine Learning algorithm on a set of data to predict the result of combinations of features.
